Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.74,0:00:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait wait,\Ndon't shoot me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Hideo Araki,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.92,0:00:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,someone killed me to keep me quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have a dream\Nabout getting shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.81,0:01:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.83,0:01:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you think I\Nwouldn't notice or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.82,0:01:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,While it's still in your head
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll probably\Nkeep on seeing those dreams, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:01:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Life's a lot longer than you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.93,0:02:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You should probably hurry up with\Ngetting that operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.92,0:02:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...What?\N- You're actually a really nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.85,0:02:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you only JUST realize that?\N- Yep, just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.91,0:02:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do people go\Nwhen they die?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I was involved in an incident\Nwhere a bullet was shot into my head,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,it swerved around inside\Nand lodged between an artery
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,saving my life miraculously.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.86,0:02:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But the operation to remove the bullet\Nis dangerous so
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.72,0:02:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,for now I've decided\Nto live with it inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:02:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And as a result...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.91,0:02:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can talk to the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.87,0:03:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Otsukare-sama desu.\N- Otsukare-sama desu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard a former-officer was murdered...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He was in the Fifth Division of\Nthe organized crime department.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.78,0:03:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifth Division...\NThat means he handled guns and drugs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.82,0:03:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.\N- What do you mean by
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.79,0:03:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"former-officer"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.96,0:03:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He injured his knee during work\Nand had to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.92,0:03:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What a horrible way to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.94,0:03:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.\N- ...Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's how it looks.\NHe was shot in the head and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The entry and exit wounds\Nof the bullet are clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.96,0:04:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Only one bullet was fired\Nand it's not in his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.80,0:04:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a little bit\Nof gun powder on his skin so
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the killer would have fired from\Nwithin 50 centimeters or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oi.\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find the bullet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It was lodged in a wall nearby\Nso we removed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.82,0:04:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to\Nlift the ballistic markings?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The bullet is warped so\NI think that'd be hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.82,0:04:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The killer was probably counting on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.81,0:04:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably thought if
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.83,0:04:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,he shot close up the\Nbullet would go through
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the victim and hit something else,\Nmis-forming it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.73,0:04:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you care about the markings\NI'm guessing you think there was a prior?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.81,0:05:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's similar?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,To what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The FORMER officer part\Nis different but
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,they were both shot from\Na short distance and
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.76,0:05:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the entry on the forehead is\Nreally similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.95,0:05:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh...When he was shot...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.93,0:05:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The bullet was mis-formed then too\Nand we couldn't get the markings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting ahead\Nof yourself kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk about this\Nmore later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Araki was injured 5 years ago\Nand left investigations,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,he was then switched to clerk duties\Nat the Organized Crime Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The new role didn't suit him and
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,he barely ever even showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.83,0:06:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means that the motive
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.87,0:06:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,probably wasn't work-related.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.94,0:06:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I want the Kandori** team
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.94,0:06:30.82,Comment,,0,0,0,,** Kandori Team: Focuses on investigating the\N victim/perp's relationship. Jidori Team: Focuses on questioning\Nclose to the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to check over the incidents Araki was involved\Nwith before being injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.82,0:06:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Because a handgun was used
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,start your search from gang-related incidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make sure this killer knows\Nthat if you touch an officer
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.93,0:06:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you won't get away with it.\N- Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.82,0:07:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The heart is 320 grams.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It is similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But this isn't enough\Nto assume the killer was the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like the boss said,\Nwe're getting ahead of ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty rare\Nfor an officer to be shot
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.77,0:07:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,dead and the way they were\Nshot is the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think this\Nis a coincidence at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:08:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This former-Corporal, Ueda,\Nwas a Detective at the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.91,0:08:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikebukuro East Station before quitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that where\Ndo you think he was working?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.94,0:08:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.92,0:08:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The same as Araki,\Nthe Organized Crime Department's Fifth Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we can't really
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,label this as a coincidence anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you know Ueda's history?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.79,0:08:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I was shot. Of course I'd\Ninvestigate the incident a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How much do you\Nknow so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.90,0:08:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've investigated all the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.72,0:08:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,gang-related incidents the former-Corporal\Nwas involved in but
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.90,0:08:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I still haven't found\Nany suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.86,0:08:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd he quit the police?\NWas it scandal-related?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.81,0:08:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he willfully quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But he didn't even tell\Nhis family why.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:09:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But a little while before
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,being killed he told his\Nfamily he'd dirtied his pride as an officer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's why he did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,From hearing that\Nit sounds like he must have
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.83,0:09:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,done something really bad.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.84,0:09:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the only\Nevidence we have is the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.01,0:09:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,bullet in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess we might get
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,some more clues from this\Nnew incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try and find a connection\Nbetween the two victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.83,0:09:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your health okay at the moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Haha...I'm fine.\NDo I look okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're sore it's okay to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep persevering and\Nget used to the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:09:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you won't realize when\Nsomething really important
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:10:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,starts to hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.82,0:10:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There's some pain that isn't\Nsolved by crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I don't want it to,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,sometimes I end up drowning\Nin the pain of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.95,0:10:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Be more specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.92,0:10:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, just forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.91,0:10:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let pain control you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. I'll be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently he was borrowing money\Nfrom relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.82,0:10:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,For the last 6 months
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,he'd stopped paying alimony too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.82,0:11:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What was he using money on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.83,0:11:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Alcohol and gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.86,0:11:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He was always so reliable before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But from about 10 years ago\Nhe started getting really
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,bad with money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what\Nmight have caused that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.83,0:11:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried asking him\Nmyself once but
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.82,0:11:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,he got mad and\Nnever answered properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was definitely 10 years ago?\N- Yes, definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.99,0:11:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Our daughter will be 16 this year,\Nat the time she'd just started school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.78,0:11:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging from what his ex-wife said
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,it's probably safe to assume\Nthat Lt. Araki was involved
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,in some kind of illegal activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think Director Kamogawa\Nis right about it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.91,0:11:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,being a gang-related crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:11:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't jump to conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.72,0:12:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Go check out\Nplaces Araki frequented and
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.89,0:12:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,check if there was any trouble there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.92,0:12:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to investigate an incident\NLt. Araki was involved in 10 years ago and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.82,0:12:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There's other people doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just investigate what I'm telling you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The boss seems cranky today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.83,0:12:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stop by the toilet,\Ngo ahead without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'll go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you gunna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.91,0:12:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.91,0:13:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.91,0:13:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,About the re-questioning of\Nthe ex-wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out Araki.\NCome out and tell me who killed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.62,0:13:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you here about the police murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.59,0:14:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I have pretty good ears too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What rumors have you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.43,0:14:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently the guy that was\Nkilled didn't have a good track record.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But it wasn't anything worth killing him over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He was just
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,kind of corrupt that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.63,0:14:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So who hated him enough\Nto kill him then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't heard anything\Nabout that yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The usual.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.45,0:14:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we haven't met\Nsince that hit and run incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you need today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.69,0:14:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know much about the police?\N- A little, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.61,0:15:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a good memory right?\N- I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know something about the Organized Crime Dept.\Nfrom 10 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You would have still been\Nin university back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.63,0:15:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Which division?\N- The Fifth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.45,0:15:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have information or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.64,0:15:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember some rumors.\N- That's good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.63,0:15:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Close the store.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,10 years ago that division
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,was hunting an organization\Nthat sold drugs but
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,one team did a premises search\Nat their office and
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,someone died.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an executive of the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.62,0:15:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He was trying to escape\Nby jumping.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A check showed the team wasn't\Nat fault
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and nobody was punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.51,0:16:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So he was essentially\Nmurdered then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about that.\NIt was a long time ago too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.60,0:16:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,After all of that\Nthere was a rumor going around that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.55,0:16:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,a large amount of money\Nhad disappeared from the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.53,0:16:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Figures differed but probably
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.62,0:16:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,around 100 or 200 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.61,0:16:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And the organization\Ndidn't do anything about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.53,0:16:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the money was seized\Nby the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There would have been a lot of risk\Ninvolved in following it up,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.53,0:16:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,forgetting it was probably for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a good possibility\Nthe police team killed the executive for the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:16:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.52,0:17:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think the police\Nare THAT crooked though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.56,0:17:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,When the executive died the scene was probably
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,in a frenzy. Someone probably saw the money\Nand got ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.53,0:17:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,In the midst of it all\Nthey took it and disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And Araki was part of the team in question?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So was the former-Detective that\Nwas shot
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.51,0:17:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and killed before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.60,0:17:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people were in the team?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,5 apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.61,0:17:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know the remaining 3?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.61,0:17:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I know 1 of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A Detective named Sakai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He works at West Itabashi station now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.54,0:18:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You really know all 3, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to know\Nthem all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.67,0:18:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.63,0:18:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the one who shot me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:19:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.59,0:19:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you guys\Nare fighting over
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.61,0:19:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you still have pride\Nas an officer
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,admit your crime and repent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.62,0:19:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll probably be killed anyway if you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.55,0:19:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Who shot me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it one of the other two guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Want us to call the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.59,0:19:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.54,0:20:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.57,0:20:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oi...\N- Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.52,0:20:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The method is the same\Nas Araki's incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.51,0:20:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's definitely a serial killer\Ntargeting officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.53,0:20:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe even terrorism.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.54,0:20:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to expand to\Nextremist groups too
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.52,0:20:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and investigate more widely\Nthan just gangs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take the reigns on this one\Nand solve it at all costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.62,0:21:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? You look flustered?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.62,0:21:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So who was the one
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,starting the fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.58,0:21:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy in the suit, right?\N- Yeah, the suit guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.62,0:21:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.60,0:21:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishikawa, we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.63,0:21:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.53,0:21:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he have any other features?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.52,0:21:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was a black suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.63,0:22:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He was about as tall\Nas this Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.53,0:22:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure? He looked\Na little shorter to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.62,0:22:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.47,0:22:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So you want to investigate\Nthe teams from
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.44,0:22:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,10 years ago?\N- Do you think inside police information
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.56,0:22:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,is that easy to get?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.45,0:22:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can't do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.52,0:22:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?\NDon't quit so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.54,0:22:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that we're\Njust typical computer nerds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.63,0:22:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.48,0:22:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There ARE people\Ndigitizing police information
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.60,0:22:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.52,0:22:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What, like journalists?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.48,0:22:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.55,0:23:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always keeping\Na stock of
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.62,0:23:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,newspaper data anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.53,0:23:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of stuff\Nthat doesn't make it to the paper
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.48,0:23:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's pretty fun to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.48,0:23:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Reading this sort of stuff really\Nmakes you question society.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.53,0:23:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still good to know though.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.59,0:23:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.56,0:23:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.53,0:23:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.52,0:24:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why're you here kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.54,0:24:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted some advice before work
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.49,0:24:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,so I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.64,0:24:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.51,0:24:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a nice house.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.47,0:24:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, my wife's family\Nis actually pretty wealthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.62,0:24:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She makes me do a lot\Nof chores at home because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.46,0:25:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How long have you been\Nan officer for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.53,0:25:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Around 25 years.\NIt's almost like a marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.68,0:25:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised I've made it\Nwithout getting a divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.59,0:25:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the toughest thing\Nup until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.53,0:25:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's really changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.53,0:25:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Not being able to solve an incident\Nis probably the toughest part.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.58,0:25:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the same right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.62,0:25:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.59,0:25:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, where'd you transfer to\Nafter your initial patrol time?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.51,0:25:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.62,0:25:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.60,0:25:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you want advice for?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.52,0:25:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about the bullet in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.53,0:26:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor is really\Nstrongly recommending the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.68,0:26:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohhh.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.52,0:26:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...So what're you gunna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.62,0:26:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm going\Nto get it done soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.49,0:26:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty dangerous, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.63,0:26:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah there's only a\N50 percent chance of success.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.50,0:26:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.50,0:26:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.55,0:26:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But the only clue left is the bullet\Ninside my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.51,0:26:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to catch the criminal, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.58,0:26:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It could also be a link to the\Ncurrent investigation too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.57,0:26:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.59,0:26:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopefully the operation goes well.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.64,0:27:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.58,0:27:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Sakai's body, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.65,0:27:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.43,0:27:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,When is it going back to\Nhis family?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.52,0:27:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,On tomorrow afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.52,0:27:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you try and make\Nit later somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.64,0:27:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.53,0:27:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you why but
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.58,0:27:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,it's to help with\Nthe investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.60,0:27:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you'll find\Nany new facts or
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.62,0:27:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,evidence on that body.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.59,0:27:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.53,0:27:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How much later then?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.51,0:27:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A week.\N- That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.57,0:27:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, 5 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.60,0:27:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NI'll try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.52,0:27:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.63,0:27:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll tell me the\Nreason one day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.62,0:28:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.51,0:28:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You look as enthusiastic as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.52,0:28:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My job is pretty much my hobby,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.49,0:28:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.52,0:28:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do you need today?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.59,0:28:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to prepare somewhere for me.\N- What kind of place?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.44,0:28:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A place where
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.49,0:28:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,no one will be able\Nto hear what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.51,0:28:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of things are going\Nto happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.53,0:28:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Matters of life and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.57,0:28:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.61,0:29:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.60,0:29:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.53,0:29:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.63,0:29:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something to talk to you about,\NDirector Kamogawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.53,0:29:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's finish this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.62,0:29:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.52,0:29:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear\Nfrom my squad leader already?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.52,0:29:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,About the operation? It's all pretty sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.59,0:29:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I couldn't bring myself\Nto talk about it until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.50,0:29:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're on a pretty big case\Nat the moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.62,0:30:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,do you think it's a good time for surgery?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.60,0:30:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it is pretty important\Nfor your health though.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.54,0:30:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So when is the operation?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.57,0:30:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In 4 days time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.64,0:32:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you follow me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.46,0:32:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,To kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.48,0:32:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishikawa, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.53,0:32:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you going to
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.50,0:32:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,make me disappear\Nand throw away
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.47,0:32:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,my body away somewhere\Nwith the bullet in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.54,0:32:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.49,0:32:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard from him that you\Nwere acting strange lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.53,0:32:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,so I was worried\Nand have been monitoring you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.58,0:32:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here too boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.53,0:32:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is one of you
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.53,0:33:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the person who shot me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.52,0:33:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous. Why would I shoot you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.49,0:33:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,When that organization's executive
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.51,0:33:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,died and the money disappeared\Nthe team that searched the office
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.56,0:33:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,was you two,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.48,0:33:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ueda who died,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.50,0:33:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Araki
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.64,0:33:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and Sakai.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.56,0:33:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you kill them?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.60,0:33:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of the money and a falling out?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.52,0:33:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, 10 years ago\Nwe were on a team together.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.49,0:33:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We searched the office\Nand someone 
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.53,0:33:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,ended up dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.52,0:33:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't remember\Nanything about money.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.55,0:33:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.66,0:33:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichikura, say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.61,0:34:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any evidence that\Nour team took the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.62,0:34:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.60,0:34:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.54,0:34:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I lied about removing the bullet\Nfor evidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.55,0:34:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and tricked you both\Ninto following me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.62,0:34:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And you finally come out now...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.56,0:34:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who shot me?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.68,0:34:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who shot you and I is...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.63,0:35:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.65,0:35:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.61,0:35:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You shot me...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.61,0:35:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You shot me with this gun!?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.61,0:36:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.60,0:36:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if I shot you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.59,0:36:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You were taking\Na walk around the scene
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.51,0:36:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,without being cautious at all.\NYou're a police officer kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.62,0:36:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You deserved to get shot for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.52,0:36:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're unlucky too.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.46,0:36:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You were actually shot\Nwhere Sakai and
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.63,0:36:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I were meeting\Nthat night.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.62,0:36:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you give him the money\Nyou stole off Ueda?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.52,0:36:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.46,0:36:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd already used up the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.53,0:36:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But he suddenly started talking\Nabout pride and guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.52,0:36:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and was trying to drive me\Ninto a deep end.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.61,0:37:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And why'd you kill Araki?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.70,0:37:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he was deep in debt and\Nstarted threatening me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.49,0:37:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And you killed Sakai\Nbecause I talked with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.54,0:37:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.60,0:37:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought for awhile\Nthat he might have
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.48,0:37:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,spilled everything to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.62,0:37:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I probably\Nwould've ended up killing him regardless.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.43,0:37:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So to protect yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.60,0:37:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you killed your own friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.70,0:37:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If they were friends they\Nwouldn't have betrayed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.46,0:37:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He obviously felt wrong\Nabout it too but
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.63,0:37:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,he pretended nothing happened\Nto stay safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.62,0:38:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.57,0:38:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no evidence that\Nyou guys took the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.57,0:38:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I COULDN'T do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.62,0:38:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you there\Nwhen the money was stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.67,0:38:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I stayed at the dead\Nexecutive's scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.53,0:38:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I made sure you were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.48,0:38:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then he was just\Nlike you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.55,0:38:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All he cared about was justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.62,0:38:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he wouldn't participate.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.41,0:38:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And where is he for it?\NHe suspected me the whole time
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.51,0:38:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but never did anything about it.\NHe's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.60,0:38:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you scared of being killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.61,0:39:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.56,0:39:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...What?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.41,0:39:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you stay in the police\Nlonger you'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.50,0:39:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much of our
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.52,0:39:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,lives we give up to do our job properly
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.71,0:39:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll never be rewarded for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.45,0:39:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We're paid the minimum and
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.62,0:39:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll end up living off pensions\Nwhen we're old.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.54,0:39:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the money we stole
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.51,0:39:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,was destined to be\Nhanded over to the country
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.56,0:39:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and used by politicians
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.53,0:39:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,on things that don't even\Nmake sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.52,0:39:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural\Nfor people like us to 
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.61,0:39:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,have it in our hands instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.51,0:39:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishikawa, one day you'll\Ngive up on justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.48,0:40:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,When that time comes you'll\Nneed people
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.52,0:40:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to support you so\Nthings don't get out of hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.51,0:40:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help you with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.52,0:40:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure that your\Ncareer goes smoothly from here on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.53,0:40:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Ichikura.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.44,0:40:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way you have no\Nevidence we stole the money or
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.63,0:40:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that I killed Ueda and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.60,0:40:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.70,0:40:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have the bullet in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.53,0:40:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you don't think I can't\Nhave the bullet switched?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.48,0:41:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus I'm a Director,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.52,0:41:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can change the direction\Nof investigations too.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.54,0:41:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about it.\NEven this time
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.61,0:41:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I managed to convince everyone it was all\Nthe work of a gang or terrorists.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.60,0:41:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys just need to\Nkeep quiet and listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.58,0:41:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.63,0:41:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Give that back.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.58,0:41:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.61,0:41:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.54,0:41:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!\NHitting him is a waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.61,0:41:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you bash him up too bad\Nwe'll get questioned about it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.59,0:42:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.61,0:42:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.55,0:42:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hit him too!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.60,0:42:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No! That's enough! Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.65,0:42:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we have evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.53,0:42:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'll\Never forget about justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.52,0:43:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Before he was talking
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.45,0:43:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,about someone "finally coming out"\Nor something.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.49,0:43:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It was weird. Did you hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.56,0:43:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.46,0:43:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He's done it a few times\Nup until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.50,0:43:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think that
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.63,0:43:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the bullet in his head\Nmight be affecting him?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.46,0:43:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that\Nyou'd actually shoot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.61,0:43:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I was freaking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.66,0:43:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost did...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.60,0:43:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure how I was\Nable to control myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.60,0:43:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think I was the gunman?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.50,0:43:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually wasn't really sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.47,0:43:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I saw you taking out the\Ntrash I decided to trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.60,0:43:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You dumb ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.53,0:44:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it all to get\Nevidence out of Director Kamogawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.50,0:44:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.50,0:44:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I can let it go this one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.52,0:44:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't ever\Ntry and trick me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.51,0:44:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.54,0:44:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking about what's going to happen\Nnext is depressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.52,0:44:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you gunna\Ndo about the bullet?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.57,0:44:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's not\Nneeded as evidence anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.61,0:44:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about it carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.60,0:44:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.64,0:45:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you made a decision yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.53,0:45:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm working for darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.51,0:45:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're\Ntrying
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.46,0:45:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,desperately to protect\Nmisguided "justice".
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.53,0:45:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're destined to lose to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.60,0:45:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll catch you.
